video.title: Teen Mom 2
video.synopsis: The highs and lows of life as new parents create more drama and heartbreak for the cast of "16 and Pregnant" Season 2 in this reality series spinoff.

episodes.synopsis: Teen mom Jenelle's partying forces her mom to take away custody of Jenelle's baby. Leah tries to work things out with the father of her twins.
episodes.title: Nothing Stays the Same

episodes.synopsis: Leah breaks down when the health of one of her twins is in question, while Chelsea starts hanging out with her ex-boyfriend.
episodes.title: So Much to Lose

episodes.synopsis: Over the Fourth of July, Jo's parents tell Kailyn to buckle down or move out, while Janelle signs over custody of Jace to her mom.
episodes.title: Change of Heart

episodes.synopsis: Kailyn is forced to borrow money from Jo to pay for school and Chelsea lets Adam move in so Aubree can have a normal family.
episodes.title: Moving In, Moving On

episodes.synopsis: Jenelle is trying to figure out how to pay for school and continues to get in trouble, while things get tough for Leah and Corey.
episodes.title: Too Much Too Fast

episodes.synopsis: Adam and Megan's fighting gets worse as Barbara helps Jenelle and invites her to Jace's first birthday party.
episodes.title: Taking Sides

episodes.synopsis: Corey surprises Leah with a marriage proposal. Kailyn lands another job. Jenelle and Kieffer search for a place to live.
episodes.title: Switching Gears

episodes.synopsis: Jenelle and Kieffer ask Barbara if they can move in with her, while Leah and Corey bring Ali in for an MRI.
episodes.title: Pushing the Limit

episodes.synopsis: Jo confronts Kailyn about dating Jordan. Leah and Corey plan for their wedding. Jenelle and Kieffer consider running off to New Jersey.
episodes.title: Slippery Slope

episodes.synopsis: Leah and Corey fight when she reconsiders the wedding. Chelsea breaks up with Adam and Kailyn settles in with her mom.
episodes.title: Two Steps Forward

episodes.synopsis: Chelsea studies for her GED, but gets distracted when she meets a new guy. Jenelle faces the consequences of taking her mom's credit cards.
episodes.title: One Step Back

episodes.synopsis: Chelsea plans for Aubree's birthday, while her dad tries to keep Adam from coming.
episodes.title: Judgment Day

episodes.synopsis: Dr. Drew hosts the cast in front of a live studio audience as Jenelle, Chelsea, Kailyn and Leah reflect on their first year of motherhood.
episodes.title: Finale Special: Check-Up With Dr. Drew

episodes.synopsis: Look back on this season's humorous and heartbreaking never-before-seen moments with Kailyn, Leah, Jenelle and Chelsea.
episodes.title: Season 1 Unseen Moments

episodes.synopsis: Jenelle bails Kieffer out of jail. Leah gets a job. Chelsea debates giving Adam another chance. Kailyn and Jordan take Issac trick-or-treating.
episodes.title: Best Laid Plans

episodes.synopsis: Leah finds out Ali must be sedated for an MRI. Jenelle is living in her car with Kieffer. Chelsea gives Adam another chance but re-tears her ACL.
episodes.title: Curveball

episodes.synopsis: Kailyn moves out without telling her mom. Jenelle files charges against Kieffer. Chelsea relies on Adam while she recovers from surgery.
episodes.title: Intensive Care

episodes.synopsis: Ali's MRI results come back. Jenelle juggles peace with her mom and dealing with Kieffer's domestic charges. Kailyn tries a new form of birth control.
episodes.title: No Looking Back

episodes.synopsis: Kailyn is alone for the holidays. Jenelle has regrets over recent events. Leah makes holiday plans. Randy bans Adam from the festivities.
episodes.title: Home for Christmas

episodes.synopsis: Ali may have a genetic disorder. Jenelle and Kieffer go to court for breaking and entering charges. Chelsea finds out that her old friend is pregnant.
episodes.title: Lean on Me

episodes.synopsis: Kieffer is upset that Jenelle hung out with an ex. Adam reverts to his old ways, much to Chelsea's dismay. Kailyn considers filing for child support.
episodes.title: Breaking Point

episodes.synopsis: Jenelle moves in with her friend after a fight with Barb. Chelsea and Adam's relationship is going downhilll. Jo confronts Kailyn about child support.
episodes.title: Making Moves

episodes.synopsis: Jenelle fights with both Kieffer and Tori. Chelsea struggles to deal with losing Adam. Leah is livid when Adam wants to buy a truck instead of moving.
episodes.title: The Beginning of the End

episodes.synopsis: Jo meets Jordan for the first time. Jenelle is sentenced to probation. Corey finds out that Leah cheated on him before their wedding.
episodes.title: Love Comes and Goes

episodes.synopsis: Jenelle goes to rehab. Chelsea works toward her GED. Leah files for divorce. Kailyn hooks up with Jordan, even though she's still with Jo.
episodes.title: Falling

episodes.synopsis: Corey arranges visitation with the girls while Leah moves her stuff out. Jenelle finds out she might be bipolar. Kailyn confesses her hookup with Jo.
episodes.title: Love Will Tear Us Apart

episodes.synopsis: Jenelle and Kailyn reflect on the past year of struggles, triumphs, legal troubles, romantic triangles and more in this episode hosted by Dr. Drew.
episodes.title: Finale Special: Check Up with Dr. Drew: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Dr. Drew chats with Chelsea, Leah, Corey and other guests to address lingering questions from Season 2.
episodes.title: Finale Special: Check Up with Dr. Drew: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: In this special episode, host Dr. Drew takes viewers through the teen mom milestones that didn't make the show.
episodes.title: Season 2 Unseen Moments

episodes.synopsis: Jenelle, Leah, Chelsea and Kailyn look back on the past year of relationship drama and parenting woes.
episodes.title: Catch Up Special
